Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: The Dull Men's Club, 1982
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wx2d
Last Broadcast Date: Boxing Day 1982
Forget chic or trendy, the founder of the Dull Men's Club says we should be proud of being boring. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less